Source: pgmnemo
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/pgmnemo/pgmnemo

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pgmnemo
Architecture: all
Provides: postgresql-pgmnemo
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-PGVERSION-pgvector
Description: Provenance-gated vector memory for LLM agents in PostgreSQL
  pgmnemo provides a provenance-gated, vector-hybrid memory substrate for LLM
  agents in PostgreSQL. It installs SQL schema objects and depends on pgvector.
